{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7004cda716","title":"在薄一波反映家乡人民公社情况的来信上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c53d57e204","index":0,"year":1959,"month":10,"day":8,"articleId":"7004cda716"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d54ab0cc80","name":"薄一波","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"3827a8760e","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"7004cda716","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"薄一波，山西省定襄县人。当时任中共中央政治局候补委员、国务院副总理。1959年10月7日他给毛泽东写信说：“我的家乡——和平人民公社的党委书记韩生智同志给我写来一封信，我看了感到十分兴奋：一、公社化后粮食大增产，工业也搞得很好；二、今年每人平均分到三十斤麦子（保证了国家征购任务后），我的家乡主粮是杂粮；三、公共食堂五十九座，看来是基本上都到公共食堂了；四、群众情绪高涨等等。特将这封令人兴奋的信打印送您一阅。”"},{"id":"34aef7a3fd","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"7004cda716","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9621d9d9db","type":"title","text":"在薄一波反映家乡人民公社情况的来信“上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"7004cda716"},{"id":"3827a8760e","type":"paragraph","text":"印发政治局书记处客同志。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"7004cda716"},{"id":"34aef7a3fd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"7004cda716"},{"id":"8095e9e361","type":"paragraph","text":"十月八日尚昆办。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"7004cda716"}],"page":{"id":"b51c5df875","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"7004cda716","start":433,"end":433}}}},"__N_SSG":true}